Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.82,0:00:03.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Previously on Fairy Tail:
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.05,0:00:07.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got trouble! Natsu's been trapped \Ninside of an artificial dragon,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.11,0:00:08.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and is getting used as its power source!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.96,0:00:11.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone wanted to try and rescue Natsu,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.11,0:00:14.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but Magnolia's facing a crisis, \Ntoo! What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.44,0:00:16.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes-yes-yes-yes-yes-yes-yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.97,0:00:19.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The real show's just getting started, ya'll!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.32,0:01:54.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Bust this thing up, and me along with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.97,0:01:58.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But if we do that, what'll \Nhappen to you, Natsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.26,0:02:00.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop making excuses!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.32,0:02:03.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If Magnolia gets ruined 'cause of me,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.69,0:02:05.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't be able to sleep at night!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.35,0:02:09.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not budging a bit, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.42,0:02:11.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.05,0:02:13.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...the city of Magnolia will be...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.51,0:02:16.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do, Erza?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.33,0:02:18.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Answer me, Erza!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.16,0:02:24.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fairy Tail Wizards!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.48,0:02:28.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard a rumor while out on a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.44,0:02:32.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That someone was trying to \Nmake an artificial dragon...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.11,0:02:35.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how it started.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.12,0:02:38.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And you secretly met with this fool?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.50,0:02:45.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She said that she was gonna capture Natsu \Nand use him as the dragon's power source.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.01,0:02:48.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And during the meeting, I \Nheard it was indestructible,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.79,0:02:54.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but for a dragon slayer's \Npower from the inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.90,0:02:57.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.17,0:03:02.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But if you hadn't handed Natsu over, that \Nmonstrosity wouldn't have been able to activate, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.96,0:03:05.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that wasn't the only reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.83,0:03:10.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Unless Natsu defeats her, the \Npeople in that city won't...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.67,0:03:12.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,People in that city?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.29,0:03:16.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That idiot went and forgot the promise he \Nmade to the people in the city without sound!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.07,0:03:21.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The guy just doesn't know when to quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.79,0:03:24.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes I'd go see how \Nhe was doing out on jobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.60,0:03:30.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But that idiot forgets everything \Nelse when he's thinking about Igneel!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.36,0:03:34.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,&#34;I'm not telling you to forget about Igneel,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.28,0:03:39.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but you must always remember your main role \Nis that of a wizard of this guild.&#34; Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.42,0:03:43.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't able to surpass Ul...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.60,0:03:47.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But him...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.08,0:03:50.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu's the kind of guy \Nwho can surpass anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.44,0:03:53.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even Igneel himself!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.31,0:03:56.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's who Natsu is!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.52,0:03:59.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If he doesn't keep getting stronger...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.30,0:04:02.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fighting him won't even be worth it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.30,0:04:04.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.83,0:04:09.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought he'd be able to destroy it easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.31,0:04:12.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me out there, Gramps.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.10,0:04:18.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.94,0:04:21.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to give you the plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.83,0:04:29.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What incredible power!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.83,0:04:32.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This power is exquisite!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.12,0:04:33.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the same...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.40,0:04:36.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...as it was back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.20,0:04:43.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw it... I definitely saw it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.44,0:04:55.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So fearsome...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.02,0:04:57.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So ferocious...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.22,0:05:00.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd never seen anything so beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.14,0:05:05.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But dragons are free spirits...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.30,0:05:08.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Since I never knew when \NI might meet one again...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.03,0:05:11.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd just make one myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.85,0:05:15.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Argh! Screw you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.73,0:05:18.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You ain't the only one \Nthat wants to see dragons!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.44,0:05:21.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So do I, and Wendy, and Gajeel!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.99,0:05:23.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But instead, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.52,0:05:25.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dragons are gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.42,0:05:27.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They're extinct.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.18,0:05:28.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a hallucination.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.93,0:05:31.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Liar, liar, liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.97,0:05:34.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No one believed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.21,0:05:36.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They laughed at me, ignored me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.42,0:05:40.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Beings of such power, dragons...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.49,0:05:43.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They kept denying they exist...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.57,0:05:47.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You must know how painful it is, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.24,0:05:49.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes-yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.77,0:05:53.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And now I've finally been able \Nto unveil this! To show everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.99,0:05:56.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, that's some messed up backstory.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.18,0:05:58.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.67,0:06:01.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,First I'll crush this city,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.13,0:06:03.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and then fly around the entire continent!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.28,0:06:09.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.47,0:06:13.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh... I should have seen this coming...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.41,0:06:15.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you the outlines \Nof what really happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.77,0:06:19.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're free to believe me or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.10,0:06:25.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap! I've got to at least stay conscious!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.33,0:06:28.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, resisting any more \Nis futile, I'm telling you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.59,0:06:31.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It ain't futile! Put some guts into it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.14,0:06:33.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.45,0:06:36.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you get what Daphne is saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.55,0:06:37.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.99,0:06:39.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You forget about our promise?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.87,0:06:41.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.10,0:06:44.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Only 6% left...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.03,0:06:45.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's about time to start, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.71,0:06:47.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes-yes-yes-yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.06,0:06:51.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,H-He forgot?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.17,0:06:53.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A promise as important as that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.24,0:06:56.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly! I'd expect that of him, but still!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.86,0:07:01.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness! Juvia \Nbelieved in you, Gray-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.86,0:07:04.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There wasn't any other method.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.81,0:07:08.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But right now, our first priority is \Ndoing something about that big thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.94,0:07:11.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do something? Like what?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.82,0:07:13.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone's collapsed!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.70,0:07:15.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the owner of the cake shop!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.20,0:07:16.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He didn't evacuate fast enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.70,0:07:17.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cover us!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.56,0:07:18.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll go save him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.06,0:07:23.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes-yes! Lizardmen 3.1 show yourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.00,0:07:25.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap! There ain't no end to 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.89,0:07:28.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What were you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.25,0:07:31.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My shop's been crushed...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.00,0:07:33.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But at least I saved this...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.33,0:07:35.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,For this, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.92,0:07:38.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You were welcoming a newcomer, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.21,0:07:42.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to lose to \Na big thing like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.85,0:07:44.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll heal him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.93,0:07:47.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Wendy! Your magic power still hasn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.56,0:07:50.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, I rested a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.63,0:07:52.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you, Wendy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.51,0:07:53.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.50,0:07:56.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.26,0:07:59.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stand pickled plums.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.65,0:08:00.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Pickled plums?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.55,0:08:03.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... They're like, my weakness.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.43,0:08:06.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone has one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.51,0:08:08.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A weakness, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.65,0:08:12.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've only just joined Fairy Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.51,0:08:15.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've only just started \Npretty much everything...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.18,0:08:20.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But I want to laugh more \Nwith Natsu, with everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.70,0:08:23.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cry with everyone, get mad with everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.21,0:08:27.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to high-five Natsu-san once again!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.64,0:08:33.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, save Natsu-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.09,0:08:34.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.80,0:08:35.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wendy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.84,0:08:38.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You fool! See what I said?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.12,0:08:44.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay, she just lost consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.94,0:08:47.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But she's used up most of her magic power...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.19,0:08:51.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Only Natsu can defeat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.52,0:08:55.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But Master told us to attack the Dragonoid...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.74,0:08:57.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.10,0:09:00.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza, Gramps gave me a secret plan...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.71,0:09:02.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I figured as much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.04,0:09:03.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to tell everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.96,0:09:09.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The rest of you, eliminate the \NLizardmen with everything you got!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.14,0:09:11.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I will take down the Dragonoid!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.44,0:09:13.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But, Erza...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.08,0:09:14.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's gonna happen to Natsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.86,0:09:19.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the master's will, therefore \Nit is Fairy Tail's will.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.55,0:09:22.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it? Protect this city, at all cost!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.81,0:09:26.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,By the honor of our guild, our very soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.69,0:09:27.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.75,0:09:32.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I know... I'm a Fairy Tail \Nwizard too, after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.50,0:09:33.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.69,0:09:34.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He-cat...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.09,0:09:39.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Juvia, come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.20,0:09:42.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Heaven's Wheel!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.12,0:09:44.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Blumenblatt!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.31,0:09:48.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes-yes... Something that weak
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.07,0:09:49.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,is not a problem at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.69,0:09:53.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,3% left until fully charged!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.75,0:09:54.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.72,0:09:59.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This thing's weak point... what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.74,0:10:01.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.71,0:10:08.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm your friend... I have \Nto save you, and yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.60,0:10:12.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.20,0:10:15.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. This should be in \Nthat thing's blind spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.33,0:10:18.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The perfect place for a counterpunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.17,0:10:19.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What exactly are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.05,0:10:23.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Juvia, I need your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.99,0:10:27.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the crucial moment to decide \Nwhether Natsu lives, or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.12,0:10:33.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't imagine a Fairy Tail without Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.51,0:10:35.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That just ain't happening!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.07,0:10:37.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.61,0:10:40.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A Unison Raid.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.54,0:10:47.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.90,0:10:52.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My magic power's about at its limit!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.07,0:10:57.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been bothering me for \Na while, but I'm sure now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.10,0:11:02.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've seen something like this before...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.64,0:11:14.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So loud!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.94,0:11:17.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! Destroy me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.59,0:11:20.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Or wait, I'm gonna destroy everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.05,0:11:21.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm not!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.13,0:11:24.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's acting odd...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.87,0:11:26.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This ain't good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.72,0:11:32.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can see it... That big thing's \Nabsorbing Natsu's soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.16,0:11:35.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Destroy me! I mean, I'll destroy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.51,0:11:37.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.80,0:11:38.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.92,0:11:43.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Out of my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.68,0:11:48.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,See? Erza's all mad now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.83,0:11:50.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.26,0:11:52.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll crush her, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.11,0:11:54.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you sayin'? She's our friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.06,0:11:56.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't matter. Gonna crush her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.57,0:11:59.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I said shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.04,0:12:01.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop arguing inside my head!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.70,0:12:02.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My, my...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.98,0:12:05.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure why we can \Nhear the whole thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.48,0:12:07.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What'll we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.70,0:12:11.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even now, he must still \Nbe affected by Nirvana...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.33,0:12:12.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're done with that already!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.78,0:12:17.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna cover for Erza, and \Ncrush all the grunts at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.49,0:12:18.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.50,0:12:22.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ice and water... I felt it before \Nwhen we faced each other,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.59,0:12:24.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but I think our magic \Npower is very compatible.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.95,0:12:26.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Compatible?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.77,0:12:30.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you believe in \Nme, I'm sure we can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.10,0:12:32.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you lend me your power, Juvia?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.57,0:12:34.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.61,0:12:40.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Magic Power Fusion!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.57,0:12:46.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Unison Raid!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.67,0:12:59.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.19,0:13:00.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A curtain of ice is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.76,0:13:07.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The lizardmen are...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.39,0:13:08.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's raining down icicles!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.68,0:13:11.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! That's cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.23,0:13:17.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I know the feeling of this magic power!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.50,0:13:19.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a Unison Raid of water and ice!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.90,0:13:22.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think Gray and Juvia...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.64,0:13:24.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They dddddddit it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.88,0:13:26.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.85,0:13:30.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Juvia.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.83,0:13:34.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Juvia is glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.09,0:13:38.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray-sama puts it all on \Nthe line for his friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.20,0:13:40.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's one reason I've come to l... l...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.77,0:13:42.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.35,0:13:45.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where'd Gray-sama go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.92,0:13:49.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at that! You gonna let him get away \Nwith stealing the juiciest scenes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.40,0:13:51.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not bad, Gray.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.31,0:13:53.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We should just crush that guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.14,0:13:55.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut the hell up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.81,0:13:57.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gettin' so pissed right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.84,0:13:59.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why don't you crush this city, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.67,0:14:00.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I said I can't, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.23,0:14:04.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I think this is getting...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.15,0:14:05.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...pretty close to the edge.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.57,0:14:07.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you hear me, Natsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.82,0:14:08.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.41,0:14:11.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're completely helpless?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.41,0:14:12.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You should be ashamed!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.86,0:14:15.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're nothing but talk, squinty eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.81,0:14:19.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How long are you gonna stayed fused in \Nthat thing, doing your one-man stand up?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.90,0:14:21.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What'd you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.63,0:14:24.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that for? That's cruel, Gray.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.38,0:14:29.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You forgot about the promise you made!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.63,0:14:32.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And you still call yourself \Na Fairy Tail wizard?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.42,0:14:35.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and destroy that dragon-thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.77,0:14:41.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes-yes... So that's what you \Nwere after, Gray Fullbuster?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.65,0:14:44.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's already too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.16,0:14:50.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Because Salamander's magic power, and \Neven most of his will itself, has been absorbed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.96,0:14:53.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If I could destroy this, \NI would've done it by now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.41,0:14:56.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Go crush that droopy eyes flat!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.04,0:14:58.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm disappointed in you, Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.57,0:14:59.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.96,0:15:05.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it so? Haven't you gotten through \Nevery challenge before by destroying stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.17,0:15:07.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't wanna hear you say stuff \Nlike &#34;Bust me up with it&#34;!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.92,0:15:13.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! Everyone... Everyone \Nin Fairy Tail needs you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.09,0:15:15.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why we're trying so hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.01,0:15:18.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A Natsu that doesn't respond to the feelings \Nof his friends isn't the Natsu I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.86,0:15:23.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy... Why, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.45,0:15:24.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's so mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.73,0:15:26.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's crush her!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.29,0:15:27.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.95,0:15:31.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're sitting there, trapped! \NYou've completely given up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.43,0:15:33.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When did I give up, exactly?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.34,0:15:34.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously though, give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.30,0:15:35.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No way, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.87,0:15:38.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You said &#34;bust me up&#34;, if I recall.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.13,0:15:40.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the same as giving up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.08,0:15:43.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing more than weakness!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.58,0:15:48.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So, just as you wish, I shall rid \Nthe world of this giant thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.09,0:15:50.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This has gotten kind of weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.48,0:15:55.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa there... Natsu's soul has \Nmostly fused with the Dragonoid!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.35,0:16:01.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just try it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.92,0:16:10.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes-yes-yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.33,0:16:13.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Lizardmen might be wiped out, \Nbut as long as I have this power...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.53,0:16:15.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.44,0:16:19.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fairy Tail has no need for those who \Nview their own life as insignificant!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.79,0:16:21.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Say that again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.20,0:16:25.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't imagine a prideful dragon ever \Nwanting to see someone as weak-willed as you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.98,0:16:30.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When you'd leap to his breast to \Nembrace him, he would smack you silly!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.50,0:16:33.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a break!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.22,0:16:36.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,With this power, couldn't we beat Erza?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.68,0:16:41.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like fun! Bring it, Erza!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.11,0:16:43.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Today, finally, I will beat you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.17,0:16:45.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, what a simpleton.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.77,0:16:49.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can hear it! He is pretty much \Nsaying exactly what he feels!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.94,0:16:51.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.07,0:16:52.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're doing impressions, {\i1}now{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.99,0:16:56.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Hey, don't move on your own!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.54,0:16:59.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You scared, Erza?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.70,0:17:02.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone like you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.14,0:17:07.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope, she's scary after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.69,0:17:10.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not enough...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.42,0:17:12.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What, that all you got?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.09,0:17:19.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I ain't kiddin' around here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.03,0:17:20.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.04,0:17:22.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The magic power being absorbed \Nis exceeding capacity!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.82,0:17:24.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.18,0:17:30.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All you guys think you can get \Naway with pushin' my buttons?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.37,0:17:33.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The flames of emotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.61,0:17:35.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.11,0:17:37.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.00,0:17:39.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, this is messed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.61,0:17:43.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I warned him and everything, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.77,0:17:48.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now the guy who's always hot under the \Ncollar has a body that's hot all over!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.50,0:17:51.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gajeel!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.10,0:17:53.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, the dolt.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.25,0:17:54.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gajeel?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.84,0:17:57.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop makin' work for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.01,0:17:58.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Secret Dragon Slayer Art!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.98,0:18:01.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Karma Demon: Iron God Sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.36,0:18:12.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gajeel...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.47,0:18:16.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like I still got a ways to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.60,0:18:21.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I was tryin' to pulverize the entire \Nthing and bust you up with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.50,0:18:25.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.37,0:18:28.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy! Call that horse guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.46,0:18:31.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Send all the fire ya got on an arrow in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.50,0:18:33.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice, Gajeel!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.09,0:18:34.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.82,0:18:37.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As it were, moshimoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.96,0:18:41.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Can everyone hear me? Anyone \Nwho can use fire, lend a hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.18,0:18:43.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.23,0:18:43.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oui!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.99,0:18:45.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We just need to send fire to Natsu, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.91,0:18:47.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Al!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.04,0:18:47.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.88,0:18:49.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can do it, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.12,0:18:53.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thrust fire into that breast \Nuntil he can eat no more!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.23,0:18:55.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're counting on you, Sagittarius!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.28,0:18:56.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Moshimoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.75,0:18:58.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Truce! I call truce!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.77,0:19:01.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't absorb any more magic power!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.61,0:19:05.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That stupid woman's insulted the \Npride and majesty of dragons.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.94,0:19:08.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't hold back. Crush her good.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.57,0:19:10.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't have to tell me twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.40,0:19:12.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now! Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.08,0:19:13.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All on one shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.36,0:19:15.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Moshimoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.00,0:19:18.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Solid Script! Heat Spell!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.42,0:19:21.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Requip, Big Bazooka!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.34,0:19:21.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Guns Magic, Blast Bullet!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.84,0:19:23.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oui!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.14,0:19:24.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Explosion!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.78,0:19:27.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu, I'll pay back my debt!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.23,0:19:34.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Take it, Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.36,0:19:52.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I've eaten, I'm all revved up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.70,0:19:58.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fired up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.22,0:20:04.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Anger! That, itself, is the \Nsource of his greatest power.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.46,0:20:05.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.32,0:20:10.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Freeing himself, and \Nstanding up to adversity...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.41,0:20:13.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the motivational power \Nhe needed to break through it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.25,0:20:17.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The best way was to make Natsu angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.48,0:20:18.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Figures!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.22,0:20:20.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We all thought the same!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.50,0:20:24.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I told Gray to make Natsu angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.95,0:20:28.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And it looks like Erza figured it \Nout without me saying anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.66,0:20:31.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, take a good look!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.84,0:20:36.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A Fairy Tail wizard is \Nridding this city of evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.35,0:20:40.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, you dragon-crazed freak! \NYou've really pissed me off now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.45,0:20:46.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead, try and use one of \Nthose &#34;Hidden&#34; techniques...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.90,0:20:49.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gettin' more power all the time here...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.59,0:20:53.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,More than you can hide from with your magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.50,0:21:00.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I finally... met one...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.73,0:21:03.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Apologize to Igneel!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.03,0:21:05.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,For this impostor dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.56,0:21:15.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Daphne's curse has been lifted!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.78,0:21:18.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Did he keep his promise?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.26,0:21:20.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That Fairy Tail wizard!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.44,0:21:24.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You see that, Igneel?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.57,0:21:27.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, the weak \Npoint of the Dragonoid...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.92,0:21:30.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...was the source of its \Npower, Natsu, himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.69,0:21:32.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.34,0:21:36.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray! You really did it this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.62,0:21:39.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It was your fault in the first place!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.72,0:21:44.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how much we fight, \Nno matter what happens,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.18,0:21:48.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,all of us at Fairy Tail need each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.22,0:21:52.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't lose even one, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.21,0:21:56.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone is looking for someone,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.17,0:21:58.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and everyone responds to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.98,0:22:05.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And that's while I'll say \Nit again: I love Fairy Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.40,0:22:07.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Lucy...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.91,0:22:08.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.26,0:22:13.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When you smile, don't people \Nsay you look like a sunfish?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.14,0:22:18.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck?! No, nobody says that!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.67,0:22:21.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You {\i1}sure{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.36,0:23:59.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu, tomorrow's finally the \Nannual cherry blossom viewing!
